Friedrich, Appellant, v. Exchange Bank of Bath County, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. May 6, 1890.) Appeal from third district court.

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Bookstaver, J.

J. L. Taylor, for appellant. H. C. Kudlich, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
